'''Nervesplicers''' were tools used to regrow damaged nerves. [[Balmorra/Legends|Balmorra]], [[Kuat/Legends|Kuat]], and [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] (including its [[Orowood Medcenter]]) were some of the only worlds in the [[Galaxy/Legends|galaxy]] where they could be found.

